			<h2>Related Selections</h2>
			<ul class="list-inline list-inline-tight"><li><a href="/topics/poverty" class="xsmall link-alt link-text">Poverty</a></li><li><a href="/topics/food" class="xsmall link-alt link-text">Food</a></li><li><a href="/topics/christianity" class="xsmall link-alt link-text">Christianity</a></li></ul>		</div>

